 worked as the Head of the Pacific Department at the Foreign and Commonwealth Office (FCO), consul general in Sydney.\n\nHe also served as Director General of Trade and Investment in Australasia.\n\n(With inputs from Agencies)","title":"Former British Ambassador to Nepal Richard\u2019s body found - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/01/124162/","video":[]}
